metadata.name: Ｃｏｔｔｏｎ Ｈａｍｉｌｙ
metadata.description:
Ｃｏｔｔｏｎ Ｈａｍｉｌｙ Is a photography taken by Michael Corn captured cotton Sail O Bots and Cryptopochi NFT collections and the most Dense DAO TUNGSTEN CUBE in a cotton version. 

All creatures are created hand made by mother Mom Ham.

Michael joins Hamily as a member of token Che-Yu Wu x Nobody #591 
but plans are much more bigger. 

Idea came when Michael recieved an birthday gift of first ever knitted hammy. 

Photography is a combination of hanmade art and edited photography represented Michael´s favourite NFT collection Sail -O-Bots aka Hamily created by Che Yu Wu. 

Half of proceeds goes to Mom Ham and the other will save for the OG HAMMY for Michael. 

Thank you Hamily ♥
